The theme is American Indepencence and Emily Bode is a quintessential American designer. (Also: We both grew up in Atlanta.) For this DB suit, Emily interviewed me about my family history and embroidered homages all over a sweet patchwork wool. The rose gold watch is a @jaegerlecoultre Reverso.
